comments.body:
@ripcurld0 Just do general testing, whatever you want to do, as long as it works as well as previous version, is really what we want to make sure.

Updating Karma.
If you have a fedora account, you can login and go to the link above.  After testing, put a comment in here that everything works as designed.  When your comment goes through the karma will increase.  As soon as 3 people say it works for them, it will get pushed into release.
